{"tid":1373251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【內有推論】元朗南邊圍私家車被毁　廂內放置藤條 車尾箱藏棍刀大量武器","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T15:12:44.000Z","uid":202698,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c92d92f3413c2282148e89aa6ec2529e3ff19e2a","tid":1373251,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/727-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E5%BB%82%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D-%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%81-%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%BE%E7%AE%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%A3%8D%E5%88%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F727-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%2597%25A4%25E6%25A2%259D-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2581-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%25A3%258D%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3gNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=68e2b421\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F727-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%2597%25A4%25E6%25A2%259D-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2581-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%25A3%258D%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&h=328fa7c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/727-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E5%BB%82%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D-%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%81-%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%BE%E7%AE%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%A3%8D%E5%88%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PhJTByR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhJTByR.png&h=98a7d9f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2NEzkP1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NEzkP1.png&h=838f8641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大批市民今日到「元朗一日遊」，警方下午 5 時起清場，爆發衝突<span style=\"color: red;\">。傍晚在元朗西鐵站下，近南邊圍村對出的公眾停車場咪錶位位置，有人發現該處的一輛私家車，車內有藤條及一頂有軍徽的疑似內地人員帽。車輛其後被示威者嚴重損毁，車窗被扑爛。</span><br />\n<br />\n有示威者之後撬開車尾箱，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現內藏日本刀、鐵通、木棍等武器。除了武器外，車尾箱內有數簿和信件，上面寫有非華裔裔人士的名和南邊圍地址。</span><br />\n<br />\n《香港 01》查冊後發現，車主名為 Karunanayaka Mudiyanselage, Eranda M.，他的註冊地址位於元朗八鄉錦莆路吳家村，該名男子持有本地身份證。"},{"pid":"c9d881b2aae0dc396f3588014fd80a23b85cd9a8","tid":1373251,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"香港01 clutch time 就做野幫呀爺洗白啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f276e1accd92b16d9a357a626931ecc609c162","tid":1373251,"uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">盧偉聰，你俾人架空左啦，敢唔敢拉中聯辦呀？</span>"},{"pid":"3f78abd268fa78345f740ff465eb53268c706a70","tid":1373251,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:02:31.000Z","msg":"車cam呀"},{"pid":"9fc33fe60b5fb2ed281517ab73fea6ce4c4c8a1d","tid":1373251,"uid":287392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"[知已知彼] 常見恐怖份子便裝車輛圖鑑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1373217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1373217/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c4fb8bf5c3fb4c9afad48dca8123b621a1747b2d","tid":1373251,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:08:46.000Z","msg":"伏味濃<br />\n1．何妖真係斷正比人影到同白衫人一齊<br />\n2．圍村D信箱係無人管好易比人了信<br />\n3．明撚知今日十鳩幾萬人入黎<br />\n仲放頂軍帽係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲